Subject: Narrative Digestion Layer

Description: Layer that turns weightier narrative moments into subject-layer SOP network records.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\ApertureReentryCycle.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\SubjectInquiry.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\NarrativeSubjectFileIndex.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\indexes\NarrativeSubjectFileTable.sop

& [NarrativeDigestionLayer] is the layer for digesting narrative into the SOP subject network
  + [layer_key] is narrative
  + [node_role] is N:narrative:<moment_key>
  + [edge_role] is E:digests:<moment_key>
  + [input] is turns, steps, stages, internal reflection moments, and scan events
  + [weightier_narrative] is narrative with pressure or impact intensity, repeated return, explicit correction, or causal draw
  + [second_pass_narrative] is the follow-up narrative formed from a closed reentry_springboard after aperture survey
  + [subject_declaration_pass] is the SOP pass that names or updates subjects, relations, and boundaries discovered by second_pass_narrative
  + [subject_layer_target] is the appropriate SOP subject layer where the narrative should persist
  + [output] is a subject-layer SOP record, SOP-HG graph, or residual outside note
  + [viewfinder_snapshot] is a structured capture when narrative needs commit-framed comparison, reweighing, and reframing
  + [subject_inquiry_layer] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\SubjectInquiry.sop
  + [narrative_subject_file_index] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\NarrativeSubjectFileIndex.sop
  + [narrative_subject_file_table] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\indexes\NarrativeSubjectFileTable.sop
  + [subject_file_interest_set] is the files of interest attached to narrated subjects for re-entry and deeper inquiry

  = must: digest weightier narrative into durable SOP only when it changes project understanding
  = must: digest second_pass_narrative only after the aperture cycle has closed into a reentry_springboard
  = must: route subject_declaration_pass to subject-layer records without overwriting preserved source or first-pass narrative
  = must: lead subject_inquiry_layer when a narrated subject needs file inspection before promotion
  = must: use narrative_subject_file_index when a narrative subject needs files of interest for future re-entry
  = must: preserve subject_file_interest_set as guidance, not authority or proof of meaning
  = must: preserve lighter narrative as periphery or scan trace
  = must: keep bookends and evidence paths attached
  = must: use ViewfinderSnapshot when previous reflection must be compared against current observation
  - never: rewrite prior narrative with hindsight

& [NarrativeSubjectFileMarker_NarrativeDigestion] is the subject-file marker for this narrative surface
  + [narrative_surface_key] is narrative_digestion
  + [narrative_surface_file] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\NarrativeDigestion.sop
  + [subject_key_set] is narrative_digestion, narrative_subject_file_index, narrative_led_subject_inquiry, layered_activation_inspection, sop_swarm_fabric, codex_lmstudio_orchestration_workspace, viewfinder_snapshot, aperture_reentry_cycle, repo_first_internal_scan, trailing_checksum_voice, operating_loop_tick, and subject_declaration_pass
  + [subject_file_table] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\indexes\NarrativeSubjectFileTable.sop
  + [lookup_ready_subject_set] is narrative_digestion, narrative_subject_file_index, narrative_led_subject_inquiry, layered_activation_inspection, sop_swarm_fabric, codex_lmstudio_orchestration_workspace, attention_runtime_registry, surface_periphery_inquiry_index, unified_faculty_attention, semantic_reentry_lookup, and local_sop_authority
  + [unresolved_subject_set] is subject_declaration_pass and second_pass_narrative_router

  = must: lead SubjectInquiry when a lookup-ready subject needs file inspection
  = must: query NarrativeSubjectFileTable before broad repository search when a narrated subject needs file-interest re-entry
  = must: keep unresolved_subject_set visible until stronger file-interest mapping exists
  = should: use SurfacePeripheryInquiryIndex after the subject file set is selected and deeper terms need search pointers
